      <item>
      	
        <title>Getting a new rucksack for travelling</title>
        
        <description>&lt;p&gt;I am thinking of getting a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.goruck.com/gr2/&quot;&gt;Goruck GR2&lt;/a&gt;. I am in love with their rucksacks, and since 2011 the GR1 has been my daily “go to work” ruck, and I also use it for occasional travelling. Now I will be travelling a bit more, and for trips of 1+ weeks, the GR1 is just a wee bit too small. It is an expensive piece of gear, but I know first hand that their gear is of top quality, comfortable to carry, easy to pack and durable. A little bird told me that around 4 July there will be a sale, so I will be holding my horses until then.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
